00:11:45.740 --> 00:11:48.420
because it was put into the
"Diagnostics and Statistics

00:11:48.420 --> 00:11:50.590
Manual" as a form
of mental illness.

00:11:50.590 --> 00:11:52.330
This isn't just
an academic idea.

00:11:52.330 --> 00:11:54.210
If something is in
the DSM, it means

00:11:54.210 --> 00:11:58.085
that your doctor can diagnose
you and treat you accordingly.

00:11:58.085 --> 00:11:59.460
And a lot of people
said, well we

00:11:59.460 --> 00:12:01.800
don't think homosexuality
is a form of mental illness.

00:12:01.800 --> 00:12:03.466
But as long as it
remained in that book,

00:12:03.466 --> 00:12:06.380
it technically was--
until this guy came along,

00:12:06.380 --> 00:12:08.310
Doctor E. Fryer.

00:12:08.310 --> 00:12:10.340
I'm amazed how many people
don't know his name.

00:12:10.340 --> 00:12:12.970
I didn't know his name until
I researched for this book.

00:12:12.970 --> 00:12:15.270
I've spoken to experts
on homosexual culture

00:12:15.270 --> 00:12:17.240
in this day and age
who've never heard of him.

00:12:17.240 --> 00:12:20.850
Doctor E. Fryer was a
psychiatrist, and he was gay.

00:12:20.850 --> 00:12:22.520
And he didn't
think he was crazy.

00:12:22.520 --> 00:12:24.857
And he had gay patients who
he didn't think were crazy.

00:12:24.857 --> 00:12:26.440
But he couldn't come
out of the closet

00:12:26.440 --> 00:12:28.560
because, not only would
it ruin his personal life,

00:12:28.560 --> 00:12:30.740
it would ruin his
professional life.

00:12:30.740 --> 00:12:33.600
So he gave a passionate speech
at the American Psychiatric

00:12:33.600 --> 00:12:36.630
Association's annual
general meeting in 1972

00:12:36.630 --> 00:12:40.110
under the name
Doctor H. Anonymous,

00:12:40.110 --> 00:12:45.730
wearing a rubber mask, a
fluffy wig, and a bow tie.

00:12:45.730 --> 00:12:48.810
Now he said, I am gay.

00:12:48.810 --> 00:12:49.680
I am a shrink.

00:12:49.680 --> 00:12:52.034
I don't think I suffer from
mental illness, et cetera.

00:12:52.034 --> 00:12:53.450
It's a wonderful
piece of writing.

00:12:53.450 --> 00:12:53.870
Look it up.

00:12:53.870 --> 00:12:54.536
You can read it.

00:12:54.536 --> 00:12:55.750
It's great.

00:12:55.750 --> 00:12:57.920
Now I wouldn't think
that wearing that get up

00:12:57.920 --> 00:13:00.720
