that you're sane.

00:13:00.720 --> 00:13:01.930
But it worked.

00:13:01.930 --> 00:13:02.680
It worked.

00:13:02.680 --> 00:13:07.720
And a year later they removed
homosexuality from the DSM.

00:13:07.720 --> 00:13:09.420
Imagine how much
courage it took to sit

00:13:09.420 --> 00:13:12.600
