00:13:20.140 --> 00:13:20.980
People are flawed.

00:13:20.980 --> 00:13:23.482
And sometimes smart people
think stupid things.

00:13:23.482 --> 00:13:25.190
We often think that
scientists are merely

00:13:25.190 --> 00:13:27.750
people who gather data and
present us with their best

00:13:27.750 --> 00:13:29.300
approximation of the truth.

00:13:29.300 --> 00:13:30.350
That's not true.

00:13:30.350 --> 00:13:32.680
Scientists are people, and
they bring their prejudices

00:13:32.680 --> 00:13:34.600
and their passions to the table.

00:13:34.600 --> 00:13:37.220
And sometimes it takes
bravery and rebellion

00:13:37.220 --> 00:13:40.820
to overturn
entrenched stupidity.

00:13:40.820 --> 00:13:43.370
Now let's talk about drugs.

00:13:43.370 --> 00:13:45.760
