00:14:24.790 --> 00:14:28.136
science has done for drugs, new
chemistries, blah, blah, blah.

00:14:28.136 --> 00:14:29.510
What I found way
more interesting

00:14:29.510 --> 00:14:32.210
is how science has been
influenced by drugs, starting

00:14:32.210 --> 00:14:35.290
with Nobel Prizes.

00:14:35.290 --> 00:14:37.540
Crick and Watson, it
is reputed that they

00:14:37.540 --> 00:14:41.620
