and wait for the microphone.

00:45:02.850 --> 00:45:03.664
AUDIENCE: Hi.

00:45:03.664 --> 00:45:04.330
ZOE CORMIER: Hi.

00:45:04.330 --> 00:45:05.330
AUDIENCE: Thanks for the talk.

00:45:05.330 --> 00:45:05.955
It was awesome.

00:45:05.955 --> 00:45:09.330
My name is Edyta
and I wanted to ask,

00:45:09.330 --> 00:45:11.490
what happens when
we imagine music?

00:45:11.490 --> 00:45:16.455
So you were talking
about [INAUDIBLE] can

00:45:16.455 --> 00:45:18.580
amusic people imagine music?

00:45:18.580 --> 00:45:20.580
ZOE CORMIER: Yes, that's
a really good question.

00:45:20.580 --> 00:45:23.460
They have found that when you
sit inside a brain scanner,

00:45:23.460 --> 00:45:25.220
the pattern of activity
inside your brain

00:45:25.220 --> 00:45:27.370
when you imagine listening
to a particular song

00:45:27.370 --> 00:45:30.690
is pretty much identical to what
happens as to when you actually

00:45:30.690 --> 00:45:31.852
hear that song.

00:45:31.852 --> 00:45:33.810
So you can just make the
music inside your head

00:45:33.810 --> 00:45:34.559
whenever you want.

00:45:34.559 --> 00:45:35.550
It looks the same.

00:45:35.550 --> 00:45:37.850
As for amusia, as
I said, there's

00:45:37.850 --> 00:45:39.030
a dozen different forms.

00:45:39.030 --> 00:45:42.875
And most people who have amusia,
they just find music confusing.

00:45:42.875 --> 00:45:45.500
And they don't really understand
what it is that the rest of us

00:45:45.500 --> 00:45:46.800
like.

00:45:46.800 --> 00:45:48.770
It depends on the
different kind you have.

00:45:48.770 --> 00:45:50.770
As I said, there's a
dozen different kinds,

00:45:50.770 --> 00:45:51.990
because there's different
bits of your brain

00:45:51.990 --> 00:45:53.410
that could be malfunctioning.

00:45:53.410 --> 00:45:54.870
And there have been
cases of people

00:45:54.870 --> 00:45:58.100
who have trained themselves
to perceive music differently.

00:45:58.100 --> 00:46:00.430
And some people who don't
perceive timbre, for example.

00:46:00.430 --> 00:46:03.140
They still enjoy rhythm.

00:46:03.140 --> 00:46:06.660
So if you have
that, go to a rave.

00:46:06.660 --> 00:46:08.690
My pleasure.

